{
  "id": "65eb17754a9420002591afd0",
  "title": "7.5 g:\\N^2\\ni (x,y)\\mapsto\\frac12(x+y-2)(x+y-1)+y\\in\\Nが全単射であることを示せ",
  "created": 1709905781,
  "updated": 1709909478,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "65eb17754a9420002591afd0",
      "text": "7.5 g:\\N^2\\ni (x,y)\\mapsto\\frac12(x+y-2)(x+y-1)+y\\in\\Nが全単射であることを示せ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709909379
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000060b057",
      "text": "from [論理と集合から始める数学の基礎 読書会]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000006d24f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000dc221f",
      "text": "7.5 [$ g:\\N^2\\ni (x,y)\\mapsto\\frac12(x+y-2)(x+y-1)+y\\in\\N]が全単射であることを示せ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17ad1280f00000ec4547",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905839,
      "updated": 1709905839
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000006b33f6",
      "text": "調べるのめんどいな……[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000a2942a",
      "text": "どちらかというと7.6以降をやりたいので、飛ばそうかな",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000006bebbc",
      "text": "文字定数を具体化して挙動を調べる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000006d5492",
      "text": " [$ g((1,1))=0+1=1]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000c6b687",
      "text": " [$ g((1,2))=\\frac12(1+2-2)(1+2-1)+2=\\frac12\\cdot1\\cdot2+2=3]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000008b1d1d",
      "text": " [$ g((1,3))=\\frac12(1+3-2)(1+3-1)+3=\\frac12\\cdot2\\cdot3+3=6]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000b3be56",
      "text": " [$ g((1,4))=\\frac12(1+4-2)(1+4-1)+4=\\frac12\\cdot3\\cdot4+4=10]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000c5d597",
      "text": " [$ g((2,1))=\\frac12(2+1-2)(2+1-1)+1=\\frac12\\cdot1\\cdot2+1=2]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000281308",
      "text": " [$ g((3,1))=\\frac12(3+1-2)(3+1-1)+1=\\frac12\\cdot2\\cdot3+1=4]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000000dfe57",
      "text": " [$ g((4,1))=\\frac12(4+1-2)(4+1-1)+1=\\frac12\\cdot3\\cdot4+1=7]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000008735a6",
      "text": " [$ g((2,2))=\\frac12(2+2-2)(2+2-1)+2=\\frac12\\cdot2\\cdot3+2=5]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000d6b9e9",
      "text": " https://www.desmos.com/calculator/jhwts82beq",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000007eb9ed",
      "text": "  放物線が動く",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000049f47",
      "text": " 表にしよ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000da7fe3",
      "text": "  table:g",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000b13c7f",
      "text": "   x\\y\t1\t2\t3\t4\t5",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000058c7f7",
      "text": "   1\t1\t3\t6\t10",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000dc5f80",
      "text": "   2\t2\t5",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000562e32",
      "text": "   3\t4",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000005e27ce",
      "text": "   4\t7",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000006785f6",
      "text": "   5",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000a623bf",
      "text": "  ！！！！！[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000028ebc3",
      "text": "  [三角数]じゃん！！！！！(激遅気づき)",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000026086d",
      "text": "\t\t\tそういうこと！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000042ff26",
      "text": "いやこれ面白い問題だな[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000053d911",
      "text": "\t[$ \\N]の話をしてるので放物線と考えるのは微妙かな…",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000697aa6",
      "text": "\t[$ t=x+y]とする、[$ h(t):=\\frac12(x+y-2)(x+y-1) = \\frac12(t-2)(t-1) = \\frac12t^2 - \\frac32t + 1]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000b402f7",
      "text": "\t[$ t]が奇数の時[$ t^2]も奇数なので、[$ h(t) \\in \\N]が言える",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000004a23ba",
      "text": "\t[$ t]を固定したまま[$ y\\in\\N]を動かせるので[$ g(x, y)]は[$ t]を固定したまま任意の整数になれる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000a57f1b",
      "text": "\t この発想なかった。見習いたい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000026bf1f",
      "text": "\tよって任意の整数[$ n]に対して[$ g(x, y) = n]であるような[$ (x, y)]が存在する(全射性)",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000087fb7a",
      "text": "\t あってるかな？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000043022b",
      "text": "\t\t\t[$ x=t-y\\in\\N]だから[$ 0<y< t]が拘束条件",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000b0cffd",
      "text": "\t\t [$ \\{z\\in\\N|h(t)<z<h(t)+t\\}]が動く範囲か",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000064c7b8",
      "text": "\t\t [$ \\bigcup_{t\\ge2\\land t\\in\\N}\\{z\\in\\N|h(t)<z<h(t)+t\\}=\\N]であれば全射性を示せる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000080ff31",
      "text": "\tえっ、単射じゃなくない？なんか勘違いしてる？？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000390a7b",
      "text": "\t [$ \\Z]ではなく[$ \\N]が変域の点？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000a02e7c",
      "text": "　　あっ、それだ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000076ef22",
      "text": "　　　上の具体例列挙を見ると、第一項は三角数なので、値の間隔から一意であることを言うのか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000001fe7b7",
      "text": "　　　本当に全単射なのかな、端が少し重なったりしそう…",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000004ecd0d",
      "text": "　　　あー、て言うか上の列挙で答え出てるじゃん、並び順がわかりにくいだけ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000bea088",
      "text": "　　　\t[\" 三角数じゃん！！！！！(激遅気づき) / そういうこと！]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000009281f9",
      "text": "　　　一般化すると",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000028d54b",
      "text": "　　　 [$ {\\rm Tri}(t) = \\frac12t(t+1)]とする。(1, 3, 6, ...)",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000377e94",
      "text": "　　　 [$ g(x, y) = {\\rm Tri}(x+y-2) + y]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000b24e1f",
      "text": "　　　 任意の自然数[$ n > 0]について[$ {\\rm Tri}(z) < n]である最大の[$ z]を[$ g'(n)]とすると",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000f7f844",
      "text": "　　　 \t[$ y=n - {\\rm Tri}(g'(n)), \\quad x = g'(n)-2 - y]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f000000057389b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこんな感じ(手抜き)",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000002e59dc",
      "text": "1つのパラメタで2次元の点を掃けるのは面白い[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000006313a7",
      "text": " [$ \\R]では成立しない……と思ったけど[ペアノ曲線]があったな",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f00000008cb600",
      "text": "気になり始めたので、こんどやろう[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb17731280f0000000df1046",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1709905781,
      "updated": 1709905781
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb23f8aff09e0000d580ce",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709908984,
      "updated": 1709908986
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb2429aff09e0000d580d1",
      "text": "\t[$ f: \\N^2\\ni (x,y)\\mapsto (a+b, a) (1\\le a < a+b, 1\\le b) ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909033,
      "updated": 1709909256
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb23f9aff09e0000d580cf",
      "text": "\t\tは全単射",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709908986,
      "updated": 1709909271
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb2517aff09e0000d580d3",
      "text": "\t[$ f': (a+b, a) \\mapsto {\\rm Tri}(a+b)+a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909271,
      "updated": 1709909403
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb2513aff09e0000d580d2",
      "text": "\t\tは全単射",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909267,
      "updated": 1709909414
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb25a6aff09e0000d580d4",
      "text": "\t(多分微妙に-1とか足りない)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909414,
      "updated": 1709909433
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb25b9aff09e0000d580d6",
      "text": "\t[$ g = f' \\circ f]なので全単射",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909433,
      "updated": 1709909467
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb25aaaff09e0000d580d5",
      "text": "\tって感じなんだろうな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909418,
      "updated": 1709909476
    },
    {
      "id": "65eb25ddaff09e0000d580d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1709909469,
      "updated": 1709909469
    }
  ]
}